men wearing silk","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not wear silk, for whoever wears silk in the world will not wear it in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2069 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/prophet-seven-commands\/","url_meta":{"origin":15292,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ahkam: Seven prohibitions and commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' ibn 'Azib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from seven things: using gold rings, silk, flax, brocade, red saddle clothes, taffeta, and silver vessels. And the Prophet commanded us to do seven things: to visit the sick, to follow the funeral procession, to bless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15210,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/wearing-silk-medical-reasons\/","url_meta":{"origin":15292,"position":3},"titl